From 4166f3461b832227af18756f82144cfe28711f85 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tamizh Chelvam Raja <tamizhr@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Sep 2025 14:24:30 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP:wifi:ath12k: Advertise SUPPORTS_VLAN_DATA_OFFLOAD for
 all frame modes

After NSS plugin modularization changes, NSS expects host to update
ppe_vp_type for a netdev. In case of native wifi mode notification
for AP_VLAN interface will not reach driver to update the vp profile.
This causing Traffic issue in WDS case. Fix this by advertising
SUPPORTS_VLAN_DATA_OFFLOAD flag for all cases. This will allow
calling ath12k_mac_op_add_interface() callback for AP_VLAN interface also

Patch dependency: 0337-01-QSDK-DP-wifi-Add-support-for-PPE-DS-Direct-switch-fe.patch

Fixes: I82f948368 ("QSDK:DP:wifi:ath12k:modularize NSS plugin interface for ath12k and PPE modules")

Signed-off-by: Tamizh Chelvam Raja <tamizhr@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c
index af6bd42..82839bd 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c
@@ -22113,10 +22113,10 @@ static int ath12k_mac_hw_register(struct ath12k_hw *ah)
 		ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORTS_TX_ENCAP_OFFLOAD);
 		ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORTS_RX_DECAP_OFFLOAD);
 
-		if (ath12k_ppe_ds_enabled)
-			ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORTS_VLAN_DATA_OFFLOAD);
 	}
 
+	ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORTS_VLAN_DATA_OFFLOAD);
+
 	if (cap->nss_ratio_enabled)
 		ieee80211_hw_set(hw, SUPPORTS_VHT_EXT_NSS_BW);
 
-- 
2.34.1

